  <brief_title>A Crossover Study With Hexalacton in Patients With Type 1 Diabetes and Microalbuminuria</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Doubleblind Placebo Controlled Crossover Study With Hexalacton in Patients With Type 1 Diabetes and Microalbuminuria</official_title>
  <sponsors>
