    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  type 1 diabetes

          -  age 18-80 years

          -  microalbuminuria

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  blood pressure&gt; 160/100 mmHg

          -  persistent macroalbuminuria

          -  pregnancy or in risc of this

          -  P-Potassium&gt;5.7 mmol/l

          -  Eplerone treatment
